<h1>Tech Growth</h1>

<h2>Source 1</h2>
<table border="1">
    <tr>
        <th>URL</th>
        <td><a href="https://datareportal.com/social-media-users">https://datareportal.com/social-media-users</a></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Author</th>
        <td>Data Reportal</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Abstract</th>
        <td>
            This site explains how social media has grown into one of the most used digital tools in the world. It shows how the number of users keeps increasing every year as more people gain internet access and as new platforms become popular. The site provides simple charts and statistics that help readers understand how quickly people have joined apps like Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, and others. It also shows how social media became part of everyday life for communication, entertainment, and business. The information helps explain why social media feels so large today and how it expanded from small websites into worldwide networks that connect billions of people across different countries and cultures.
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

